{
  "text": "Third, we determined that SMIFH2 does not allow formin to inhibit the end-to-end annealing of actin filaments ( Figure S2 ). Formin-associated filaments do not anneal [CITATION_1] . SMIFH2 allowed preassembled filaments severed in the presence of Cdc12 to anneal ( Figures S2A and S2B ) and allowed Cdc12-and mDia2-nucleated filament seeds to anneal ( Figures   S2C and S2D ). Conversely, SMIFH2 had no effect on annealing in the absence of formin ( Figures S2A and S2B ).",
